'''美洲擬庸鰈'''（''Hippoglossoides platessoides''）是一種[[比目魚|比目魚]]，屬於[[鰈科|鰈科]]。是一种好吃的鱼。美洲擬庸鰈是生活於[[大西洋|大西洋]]的[[物種|物種]]。<ref name="grolier">"Plaice." Grolier Encyclopedia of Knowledge, volume 15, copyright 1991. Grolier Inc., ISBN 0-7172-5300-7</ref>牠們分佈在南[[拉布拉多|拉布拉多]]至[[羅德島|羅德島]]，棲息深度30-2000米，為溫帶海水魚，棲息在軟底質底層水域，以小魚及[[無脊椎動物|無脊椎動物]]為食。他們會於[[緬因灣|緬因灣]]產卵，最高峰的時期介乎每年的4月和5月之間。牠們最長達70厘米。<ref name=dery>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nefsc.noaa.gov/fbi/age-man/ampl/ampl.htm|author=Dery, L.M.|title=American plaice, ''Hippoglossoides platessoides''|work=Fishery Biology Program|publisher=Woods Hole Massachusetts Laboratory of the National Marine Fisheries Service (NMFS), Northeast Fisheries Science Center (NEFSC)|accessdate=2007-01-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070311050106/http://www.nefsc.noaa.gov/fbi/age-man/ampl/ampl.htm|archivedate=2007-03-11}}</ref>[[西北大西洋漁業組織|西北大西洋漁業組織]]（Northwest Atlantic Fisheries Organization）指美洲擬庸鰈正被過度捕撈，並沒有復原的跡象。<ref name=NAFO>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nafo.int/fisheries/frames/fish-pla.html|title=Fishery Recent Assessment (2005 and 2006)|publisher=Northwest Atlantic Fisheries Organization|accessdate=2007-01-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070607020853/http://www.nafo.int/fisheries/frames/fish-pla.html|archivedate=2007-06-07}}</ref>另一方面，[[加拿大|加拿大]]政府卻相信美洲擬庸鰈數量仍很豐富，並是第二多被捕撈的比目魚，佔加拿大比目魚漁獲的50%。<ref name=FOC>{{Cite web|url=http://www.dfo-mpo.gc.ca/zone/underwater_sous-marin/plaice/plaice-plie_e.htm|title=American plaice|work=Underwater World|publisher=Fisheries and Oceans Canada|accessdate=2007-01-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070204122658/http://www.dfo-mpo.gc.ca/zone/underwater_sous-marin/plaice/plaice-plie_e.htm|archivedate=2007-02-04}}</ref> 好吃的鱼

